These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: card-games, collecting
City: london, san-francisco
1. City:london is in an even position##4
2. City:san-francisco == Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| City     | san-francisco    | london   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: prague, marseilles
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. City:marseilles is on the left of City:prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | marseilles | prague        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: ambient, house
Game: billiard, whist
1. Game:billiard is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:house is on the left of Music-Genre:ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| Game   | billiard | whist |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Beverage: 7up, lemonade
Birthday: may, april
1. Beverage:lemonade is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
2. Birthday:april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Birthday       | may | april    |

